            <li><a href="https://dev.to/bryan_maclee/null-was-a-billion-dollar-mistake-falsy-was-the-second-3o61" class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 underline">Null was a billion-dollar mistake. Falsy was the second.</a>. On <code class="font-mono text-sm bg-slate-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">n&#111;t</code>, presence as a type-system question, and why scrml refuses to inherit JavaScript's truthiness rules.</li>
            <li><a href="https://dev.to/bryan_maclee/scrmls-living-compiler-23f9" class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 underline">scrml's Living Compiler</a>. The compile-time evaluation story.</li>
